{"tid":1340834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(屯門避難所)嶺南大學開放庇護站","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:05:50.000Z","uid":51200,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5873c9f47db79495b0a4e534527f9f55e4cf7c4e","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"【7.21 嶺南開放庇護站事宜】<br />\n嶺南大學康樂樓2樓屬於學生會管理，現開放2樓空地予有需要人士暫作休息，避免受不必要滋擾及攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n地址：屯門青山公路嶺南段8號<br />\n時間：即時至翌日<br />\n<br />\n請不要逗留在元朗站，直接由兆康站前往嶺南，並於北閘進入。<br />\n<br />\n條命要緊<br />\n冇地方去嘅匿入去<br />\n雲海話班黑社會好似轉場去天水圍屯門打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb6ec3e8b9fc7b377649bc72e2d69ba53f619da","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"8ef6b01626883d9960ad4e1e51f2a9082378c3f8","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"走難呀走難呀"},{"pid":"3a4e10f5c30270dc366f3c7f48a293a9c791ac05","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"5646347a94d295ffd392aa2a7e93eb832afe4eb9","tid":1340834,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"天水圍好似開咗波"},{"pid":"02301fc3c7b633c3c2f3e93df93c97d11b1960eb","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56747f0fe3aa5390e04c73601c6b3e7a9c1e0e2","tid":1340834,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5646347a94d295ffd392aa2a7e93eb832afe4eb9","tid